int shmget(key_t key, size_t size, int flag)
shmat-process can link its own memory with shared memory space
void *shmat(int id, cast void *shmadd, int flag)

int id;
id = shmget(IPC_PRIVATE, 4, IPC_CREAT/0666);

int *ptr;
ptr = (int*)shmat(id,0,0);

size-byte space 0666-r/w permission to user, owner and others


